{"tid":2263693,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"歷代級合作！Rain 鄭智薰 & JYP 朴軫永將以雙人組席捲樂壇～","createTime":"2020-10-30T05:32:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-30T11:38:11.000Z","uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"08b6736b65d07851a136c7c4eafb8fe91674796e","tid":2263693,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T05:32:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/800_86400_66a0238658172cdb0cd044cf088b4da2/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-10-30/131291-882664.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F800_86400_66a0238658172cdb0cd044cf088b4da2%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-10-30%2F131291-882664.jpg&h=fc242bdc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nOMG～又一組活久見！！！太想看他們倆的LIVE舞台了。<br />\n<br />\nSolo 歌手 Rain（鄭智薰）將與 JYP（朴軫永）組成雙人組合，這樣歷代級的合作也引發網友們熱烈討論。<br />\n<br />\n近期，Rain 的經紀公司就透露了他正在準備新專輯的消息，並暗示 Rain 將與「所有人都認可且擁有卓越舞蹈實力的歌手」合作，組成雙人組合。時隔三年再次發表的新專輯，因為是和舞蹈實力者的相遇，這次不僅僅是在音樂上，絕對會讓大家看到超越之前作品的，更棒的舞台。<br />\n<img src=\"https://a.ksd-i.com/s/480x_86400_50ba166595237e07a3de4b05966828b8/static.koreastardaily.com/2020-10-30/131291-882665.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fa.ksd-i.com%2Fs%2F480x_86400_50ba166595237e07a3de4b05966828b8%2Fstatic.koreastardaily.com%2F2020-10-30%2F131291-882665.jpg&h=cffa2f63&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n對於 Rain 和 JYP 的合作消息已是確定的，不過 Rain 的經紀公司也表示回歸日期尚未定案，但粉絲們已經充滿了期待。<br />\n<br />\n而曾經是 JYP 娛樂出身的 Rain，與發掘並培養他的朴軫永「老師&amp;製作人」，又會碰撞出什麼全新的火花呢？<br />\n<br />\n（圖：JYP／R.A.I.N.Company／Season B Season）"},{"pid":"211cb7e6ce9425bc70355d369f3b6f8a9f3b8ea1","tid":2263693,"uid":261849,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T05:36:50.000Z","msg":"Rain個樣仲後生個老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d027378580ee14a3fd36d82687278ca402602af0","tid":2263693,"uid":145273,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-30T05:38:22.000Z","msg":"嗰組合名係咪叫RJ?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"